Obfuscation includes **AES-encrypted strings** (e.g., key in `.rodata`) and **syscall hopping** to evade EDRs. Purge Go malware with **GOVM** (Go Virtual Machine) analysis. Real-world example: **QakBot** (CVE-2023-41760) abuses Go’s cross-platform nature.

